== Tusk*It

Is is an issue/bug tracker with Agile twist.

It is a web application written in Ruby on Rails

== What is it for?

Tusk*It is written for small teams who want to automate their work, spend less
time on overhead introduced by Agile methodologies and still enjoy all the benethits of Agile practices.

== Install

- Download tar.gz or zip file and uncompress it

- Install as any other RoR application and cd to the tuskit directory

- Copy config/database.yml.example to config.database.yml and change settings

- Copy config/config.yml.example to config.yml and change settings

- run ./script/admin_create

- run ./script/server

- point your browser at http://0.0.0.0:3000

- login and start using it




